    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TheGiddyLimit/homebrew/master/_img/GHMG/ShatterCorpse.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TheGiddyLimit/homebrew/master/_img/GHMG/ShatterCorpse.webp\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"rd__quote\"><p class=\"rd__quote-line \">“<i>The sound of breaking glass startles most, but think twice before going to see what caused it if it is followed by the sound of moaning.</i>”</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Covered in Glass.</span></span> <p>When someone dies with glass embedded in their skin—such as being stabbed by a shard of glass or killed by a falling window—they may rise as a shatter corpse. Shards of glass continually grow through the skin of a shatter corpse, covering them in razor-sharp weapons.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"2\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Ponderous and Noisy.</span></span> <p>Shatter corpses are no more mobile than an average zombie, and the constantly breaking glass makes them even easier to hear coming.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Dangerous Volley.</span></span> <p>Shatter corpses can flick hails of glass shards at nearby creatures. The shards grow back within a few seconds.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"4\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Salvage</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \">p304</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable no-select no-print lst-is-exporting-image__hidden\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\" title=\"Toggle Visibility (CTRL to Toggle All)\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>The glass from ten shatter corpses can be used to create a suit of @item[glass-studded armor|GHMG] <span class=\"rd-homebrew__disp-inline\" data-plut-hover=\"true\" data-plut-hover-inline=\"true\" data-plut-hover-inline-entry=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;entries&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Homebrew Modifications&quot;,&quot;entries&quot;:[&quot;{@b The following text has been removed with this homebrew:}&quot;,&quot;(see Chapter 4)&quot;]}\">[...]</span> with a successful [[/save ability=dexterity dc=10]] (&amp;Reference[skill=SleightofHand]{Sleight of Hand}) check by someone proficient with @item[jeweler's tools|PHB]. Crafting this item takes 10 days and costs 1000 gp.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"5\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Lore</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \">p304</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable no-select no-print lst-is-exporting-image__hidden\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\" title=\"Toggle Visibility (CTRL to Toggle All)\">[–]</span></span></h3> <div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">[[/save ability=intelligence dc=10]] (&amp;Reference[skill=Religion]):</span></span> <p>Shatter corpses are a stronger kind of zombie that arises when someone dies from being impaled on broken glass.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"7\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">[[/save ability=intelligence dc=15]] (&amp;Reference[skill=History]):</span></span> <p>Those that attempt to use a melee attack against a shatter corpse are likely to cut themselves unless they attack with carefully.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"8\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">[[/save ability=intelligence dc=20]] (&amp;Reference[skill=Arcana]):</span></span> <p>Shatter corpses can launch volleys of broken glass.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div>",
